6月10日，多艘船只在[[普罗维登西亚岛|普罗维登西亚岛]]东南偏东约105公里海域发现西南[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]上空出现本季第一个热带低气压<ref name="Partagas">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1901-1904/1904.pdf | title = Year 1904 | author = Jose F. Partagas | date = 1997 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | location = Miami, Florida | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406105418/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1901-1904/1904.pdf | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋向[[罗盘方位|东北偏北]]移动并缓慢增强，于6月12日清晨达到热带风暴强度。转向东北后，风暴进一步强化，于6月13日达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的一级飓风标准，再于数小时后达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里，最低[[气压|气压]]1003[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.6[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref><ref name="meta" />不过，上述风速及气压数据都是由古巴气象研究所的拉蒙·佩雷斯（{{lang|pt|Ramón Perez}}）于2000年推断得出<ref name="meta" />。不久后，飓风从古巴[[格拉玛省|格拉玛省]][[皮隆_(古巴)|皮隆]]附近登陆，再于6月14日清晨减弱成热带风暴。气旋很快就进入[[大西洋|大西洋]]，但仍在继续弱化，强度于当天回落至热带低气压标准，并且当晚就在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]东南部上空逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

由于飓风移动缓慢，[[牙买加|牙买加]]西部降下超过250毫米雨量，随之而来的洪灾将部分道路淹没，多座桥梁冲毁，部分地区同外界的交通中断<ref>{{cite report | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/032/mwr-032-06-0273a.pdf | title = Cyclonic Depression and Flooding in Jamaica | author = Maxwell Hall | date = 1904-06-15 | work = Weather Bureau | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | page = 273 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161105035314/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/032/mwr-032-06-0273a.pdf | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-11-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。古巴东部也降下暴雨，[[圣地亚哥-德古巴|圣地亚哥-德古巴]]仅五小时就测得约360毫米雨量。约有150户民居受损或被毁，许多矿山、公路和铁路受到影响。[[科布_(古巴)|科布]]（{{lang|en|El Corbe}}）是受灾最严重的城市之一，市内的低洼地区被完全摧毁，同样被毁的还有铁轨和公、铁路桥梁。<ref name="nyt618">{{cite news | title = Storm Killed Over 100 | date = 1904-06-18 | newspaper = The New York Times | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | location = Santiago de Cuba, Cuba | publisher = The New York Times Company | url = http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1904/06/18/104978715.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1481706654&Signature=7i8hFm7nwjWJC3Bztf2Pd%2FxPDYk%3D | archivedate = 2016-12-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161214090627/http://article.archive.nytimes.com/1904/06/18/104978715.pdf?AWSAccessKeyId=AKIAJBTN455PTTBQQNRQ&Expires=1481706654&Signature=7i8hFm7nwjWJC3Bztf2Pd%2FxPDYk%3D }}</ref>该国至少有87人丧生<ref name="25deaths">{{cite report | title = The Deadliest Atlantic Tropical Cyclones, 1492-1996 | date = 1997-04-22 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | author = Edward N. Rappaport | author2 = Jose Fernandez-Partagas | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160907054020/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyapp1.shtml | publisher = National Hurricane Center | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pastdeadlyapp1.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-09-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，还有来源估计死亡人数超过250<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5661750/the_wilkesbarre_record/ | title = Cuba Swept by a Great Storm | date = 1904-06-17 | newspaper = The Wilkes-Barre Record | page = 1 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | location = Santiago de Cuba, Cuba | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928001350/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5661750/the_wilkesbarre_record/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。
