经过三个月的沉寂，[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东北方向约680公里洋面出现第二场热带风暴<ref name="Partagas" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。气旋连续数天向西北移动并缓慢增强，到[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]9月12日中午12点已增强成飓风。六小时后，气旋达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时130公里的最高强度，然后在{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月14日下午13点左右以最高强度登陆[[南卡罗莱纳州|南卡罗莱纳州]]雪松岛（{{lang|en|Cedar Island}}）。<ref name="HURDAT" />登陆点测得985毫巴（百帕，29.1英寸汞柱）气压，这也是地面测得的风暴最低气压值<ref name="u.s. hurricanes">{{cite report | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | title = Chronological List of All Hurricanes: 1851 – 2015 | date = 2016 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | archivedate = 2016-11-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161113005842/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。约五小时后，飓风减弱成热带风暴并突然向东北大幅转向。风暴逐渐减弱并失去[[热带气旋|热带天气系统特征]]，于9月15日清晨在[[特拉华湾|特拉华湾]]上空转变成温带气旋。温带残留短暂强化，风速达到一级飓风标准，最终于当晚在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]上空逐渐消散。<ref name="HURDAT" />

南卡罗莱纳州[[查尔斯顿_(南卡罗莱纳州)|查尔斯顿]]近海有三艘渔船沉没，致使多人溺毙，另外还有一艘船倾覆，导致三人遇难<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Charlotte News | date = 1904-09-14 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Lost In Gale | location = Charlotte, South Carolina | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386702/the_charlotte_news/ | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928004902/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386702/the_charlotte_news/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]][[新汉诺威县|新汉诺威县]][[莱茨维尔比奇_(北卡罗莱纳州)|莱茨维尔比奇]]（{{lang|en|Wrightsville Beach}}）另有两人溺亡<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Wilmington Morning Star | date = 1904-09-14 | publication-date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Two Fishermen Drowned | location = Tarboro, North Carolina | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386966/the_wilmington_morning_star/ | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927230706/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386966/the_wilmington_morning_star/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。飓风催生出的一场龙卷风导致约20户民宅被毁，另有多幢建筑受损，其中单几家轧棉厂的损失数额就有25000美元，[[芒特奥利夫_(北卡罗莱纳州)|芒特奥利夫]]（{{lang|en|Mount Olive}}）至[[费森_(北卡罗莱纳州)|费森]]（{{lang|en|Faison}}）有许多电线杆倒塌，一人伤重不治<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Wilmington Morning Star | date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Storm Disasters | location = Wilmington, North Carolina | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386953/the_wilmington_morning_star/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928000518/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386953/the_wilmington_morning_star/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = News and Observer | date = 1904-09-13 | publication-date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Carolina Beneath The Rush Of A Tempest | location = Goldsboro, North Carolina | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386754/news_and_observer/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928001259/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386754/news_and_observer/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。风暴还在该州催生出另外两场龙卷风，都引发情况类似的破坏<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = News and Observer | date = 1904-09-14 | publication-date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Clouds Met At Durham | location = Durham, North Carolina | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386768/news_and_observer/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928003245/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386768/news_and_observer/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = News and Observer | date = 1904-09-14 | publication-date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Ruin Marks Three Miles | location = Warrenton, North Carolina | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386768/news_and_observer/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928003245/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386768/news_and_observer/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。南、北卡罗莱纳州部分地区降下暴雨，其中南卡罗莱纳州史密斯米尔斯（{{lang|en|Smiths Mills}}）雨量达到230毫米<ref name="rainfall">{{cite report | title = Rainfall Associated With Hurricanes (And Other Tropical Disturbances) | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | publisher = United States Weather Bureau's National Hurricane Research Project | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | author1 = R. W. Schoner | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065316/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/1956NHRPreportNo3.pdf | author2 = S. Molansky | page = 222 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | format = PDF | date =  }}</ref>。[[马里兰州|马里兰州]]因狂风导致大面积地区的树木、庄稼和输电线缆受损，[[巴尔的摩|巴尔的摩]]有一人触电身亡。[[切萨皮克湾|切萨皮克湾]]有许多船只受损、搁浅或倾覆。<ref name="TSLH_2">{{cite news | newspaper = The Salt Lake Herald | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Havoc At Baltimore | location = Baltimore, Maryland | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386500/the_salt_lake_herald/ | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927232236/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386500/the_salt_lake_herald/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>

[[特拉华州|特拉华州]]有九人死亡，其中八人死于拖船沉没，一人死于[[双桅纵帆船|双桅纵帆船]]搁浅<ref name="TSLH_1">{{cite news | newspaper = The Salt Lake Herald | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Atlantic Coast Swept By Gale | location = New York, New York | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386474/the_salt_lake_herald/ | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927235138/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386474/the_salt_lake_herald/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref name="TEJ_1">{{cite news | newspaper = The Evening Journal | date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Ashore At Breakwater | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5387032/the_evening_journal/ | location = Lewes, Delaware | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927233408/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5387032/the_evening_journal/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。[[刘易斯_(特拉华州)|刘易斯]]部分民居和商铺的屋顶被狂风掀开，还有部分树木倒塌，电报、电话线路中断<ref name="TEJ_1" />。[[费城|费城]]和[[纽约|纽约]]降下暴雨，许多街道和地下室被淹<ref name="TSLH_3">{{cite news | newspaper = The Salt Lake Herald | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Unprecedented Rainfall | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania | via = Newspapers.com | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386559/the_salt_lake_herald/ | page = 1 | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927230356/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386559/the_salt_lake_herald/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Fort Wayne Sentinel | date = 1904-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Philadelphia Deluged | location = Philadelphia, Pennsylvania | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5475917/the_fort_wayne_sentinel/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928003642/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5475917/the_fort_wayne_sentinel/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref><ref name="TFWS_1" />。纽约的风速达到每小时130公里，致使成百上千的窗户破损，还有许多树木倒塌，电缆中断，一名男子被铸铁制成的防火梯砸中后身亡<ref name="TFWS_1">{{cite news | newspaper = The Fort Wayne Sentinel | date = September 15, 1904 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = East Is Swept By Damaging Storm | location = New York, New York | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5475968/the_fort_wayne_sentinel/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927235636/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5475968/the_fort_wayne_sentinel/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。[[纽约港|纽约港]]有19艘驳船的锚系脱落，另有多艘小船在风暴期间搁浅<ref name="TSLH_1" />，[[波士顿|波士顿]]也有15艘船受损或搁浅。[[新英格兰|新英格兰]]南部各地在狂风肆虐下有大面积树木和大量电缆受损<ref name="TSLH_5">{{cite news | newspaper = The Salt Lake Herald | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Gale At Boston | location = Boston, Massachusetts | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386633/the_salt_lake_herald/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927230904/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386633/the_salt_lake_herald/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>，整个美国的损失总额至少有200万美元<ref name="Partagas" />。[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]的电话和电报服务受狂风干扰<ref name="ET_1">{{cite news | newspaper = The Evening Telegram | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-21 | title = Worst Storm In Thirty Years | page = 3 | location = North Sydney, Nova Scotia}}</ref>，[[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]有一名女性被倒塌的树木砸中后死亡<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Scranton Truth | date = 1904-09-16 | publication-date = 1904-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Halifax Saved By Wind's Shift | location = Halifax, Nova Scotia | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5464860/the_scranton_truth/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927233321/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5464860/the_scranton_truth/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。哈利法克斯的消防员此次正力图扑灭一场大火，气旋产生的狂风对此颇有助益，但火灾依然造成约50万美元的损失<ref name="TSLH_6">{{cite news | newspaper = The Salt Lake Herald | date = 1904-09-15 | publication-date = 1904-09-16 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Shift Of Wind Saved The Town | location = Halifax, Nova Scotia | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386667/the_salt_lake_herald/ | page = 1 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180928000217/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5386667/the_salt_lake_herald/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。加拿大大西洋省份有多艘船只沉没或搁浅，还有船只不得不返回包括[[新不伦瑞克|新不伦瑞克]]、[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]和[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]在内的港口暂避<ref name="ec">{{cite report | url = http://www.ec.gc.ca/Hurricane/default.asp?lang=en&n=6FBA4C35-1 | title = 1904-2 | date = 2011-11-24 | publisher = Environment Canada | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | archivedate = 2016-11-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161120193356/http://www.ec.gc.ca/hurricane/default.asp?lang=En&n=6FBA4C35-1 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | newspaper = The Inter Ocean | date = 1904-09-18 | publication-date = 1904-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-12-14 | title = Hurricane Damages Boats | location = St. John's, Newfoundland | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5485185/the_inter_ocean/ | page = 3 | via = Newspapers.com | archive-date = 2018-09-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180927233908/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/5485185/the_inter_ocean/ | dead-url = no }}{{open access}}</ref>。
